      "Hydrated salts: contain water of crystallization",
      "Anhydrous: without water of crystallization",
      "Hard water: contains Ca²⁺ and Mg²⁺ ions",
      "Temporary hardness: removed by boiling",
      "Permanent hardness: removed by washing soda or ion exchange"
    ]
